            "id": 6008727,
            "title": "晶技5月營收月減13.31% Q2估維持成長",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>頻率元件龍頭廠晶技 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3042:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3042\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3042-TW</a>) 受<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/usdtwd\">新台幣</a>升值壓力及客戶端拉貨動能下降，今 (5) 日公布 5 月營收下滑至 11.01 億元，月減 13.31%，年增 12.63%，但這也大符合晶技歷年在第二季淡季裡的單月營收走勢。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008727%2Fl%2F90cedbfe0c71def0c197a9d68a20f680.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008727%2Fl%2F90cedbfe0c71def0c197a9d68a20f680.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008727%2Fl%2F90cedbfe0c71def0c197a9d68a20f680.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008727%2Fl%2F90cedbfe0c71def0c197a9d68a20f680.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008727%2Fl%2F90cedbfe0c71def0c197a9d68a20f680.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008727%2Fl%2F90cedbfe0c71def0c197a9d68a20f680.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008727%2Fl%2F90cedbfe0c71def0c197a9d68a20f680.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008727%2Fl%2F90cedbfe0c71def0c197a9d68a20f680.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008727%2Fl%2F90cedbfe0c71def0c197a9d68a20f680.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008727%2Fl%2F90cedbfe0c71def0c197a9d68a20f680.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008727%2Fl%2F90cedbfe0c71def0c197a9d68a20f680.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008727%2Fl%2F90cedbfe0c71def0c197a9d68a20f680.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008727%2Fl%2F90cedbfe0c71def0c197a9d68a20f680.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008727%2Fl%2F90cedbfe0c71def0c197a9d68a20f680.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008727%2Fl%2F90cedbfe0c71def0c197a9d68a20f680.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008727%2Fl%2F90cedbfe0c71def0c197a9d68a20f680.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008727%2Fl%2F90cedbfe0c71def0c197a9d68a20f680.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">晶技執行長林萬興。(鉅亨網記者張欽發攝)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>晶技 2025 年 1-5 月營收 55.39 億元，年增 17.19%，6 月有客戶盤點因素干擾，營收可能較 5 月下滑，法人估計，晶技第二季營收呈現季成長，也較去年同期成長。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>晶技在關稅及匯率的干擾之下，已積極檢討生產成本壓力，對於新料號產品報價重新審視，若決定加以調整，最快將在第三季開始執行，也期望在出貨結構上的高階產品出貨量提升，有助於獲利的改善。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>晶技在海外的新增生產基地已於去年第四季起陸續投產，其中並以浙江寧波的晶創電子車用頻率元件生產最先投產，而在印尼洒水的新設置生產基地，並已經投產，產能在積極求拉升，以先達到每月 2000 萬顆石英元件後再行擴張。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
