            "id": 6008640,
            "title": "外資加碼兩檔記憶體股3.4萬張 反手調節四檔航運股",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台股今 (5) 日終場漲幅收斂，小漲 56 點，收在 21764 點，往半年線靠攏，投信終止連 12 買，並集中火力大賣台泥，外資則逢低承接，已連 10 買，累計買超張數高達 22 萬張，外資也加碼兩檔記憶體股，包括南亞科與華邦電，合計達 3.4 萬張，並調節四檔航運股。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008640%2Fl%2F231921c1f7e158214a712a1fb6916932.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008640%2Fl%2F231921c1f7e158214a712a1fb6916932.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008640%2Fl%2F231921c1f7e158214a712a1fb6916932.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008640%2Fl%2F231921c1f7e158214a712a1fb6916932.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008640%2Fl%2F231921c1f7e158214a712a1fb6916932.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008640%2Fl%2F231921c1f7e158214a712a1fb6916932.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008640%2Fl%2F231921c1f7e158214a712a1fb6916932.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008640%2Fl%2F231921c1f7e158214a712a1fb6916932.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008640%2Fl%2F231921c1f7e158214a712a1fb6916932.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008640%2Fl%2F231921c1f7e158214a712a1fb6916932.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008640%2Fl%2F231921c1f7e158214a712a1fb6916932.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008640%2Fl%2F231921c1f7e158214a712a1fb6916932.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008640%2Fl%2F231921c1f7e158214a712a1fb6916932.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008640%2Fl%2F231921c1f7e158214a712a1fb6916932.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008640%2Fl%2F231921c1f7e158214a712a1fb6916932.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008640%2Fl%2F231921c1f7e158214a712a1fb6916932.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008640%2Fl%2F231921c1f7e158214a712a1fb6916932.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">外資加碼兩檔記憶體股3.4萬張 反手調節四檔航運股。(鉅亨網資料照)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>三大法人合計賣超 65.04 元，外資買超 0.66 億元，連 2 買，自營商轉賣 40.17 億元，投信賣超 25.53 億元，終止連 12 買；期貨方面，外資小幅減碼空單 67 口，未平倉空單水位降至 37098 口。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>觀察外資買超對象，特別青睞記憶體族群與台積電，其中，兩大 DRAM 業者南亞科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2408:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2408\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2408-TW</a>)、華邦電(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2344:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2344\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2344-TW</a>) 合計張數共 3.4 萬張，並加碼台積電近 1 萬張，同時持續低接台泥(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1101:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1101\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1101-TW</a>)，大買 6 萬張，已連 10 買。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>外資賣超鎖定航運股與金控股，包括陽明 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2609:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2609\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2609-TW</a>)、長榮(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2603:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2603\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2603-TW</a>)、華航(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2610:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2610\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2610-TW</a>) 與長榮航 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2618:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2618\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2618-TW</a>) 全數都在賣超榜單上，四家合計張數高達 7.8 萬張，金控族群的中信金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2891:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2891\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2891-TW</a>)、國泰金(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2882:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2882\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2882-TW</a>)、富邦金(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2881:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2881\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2881-TW</a>) 皆遭調節，三檔共達 17 萬張。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>投信則與外資對作，大賣台泥近 7 萬張，並加碼國泰金、富邦金與中信金，三檔合計約 18 萬張，呈現你丟我撿；自營商操作也與外資反方向，逢高調節南亞科 4 千張、台積電約 7 百張。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
